PN,41301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777449958
OL,3,CWoman whose partner died suddenly from
OL,4,Cepilepsy highlights 'invisible'
OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,FA woman from Wantage whose partner
OL,8,Fdied suddenly from epilepsy is calling
OL,9,Ffor more support and awareness around
OL,10,Fthe condition.
OL,12,FJane Hanna founded the charity SUDEP
OL,13,FAction thirty years ago, along with
OL,14,Ffour other bereaved women, after her
OL,15,Fpartner Alan died suddenly.
OL,17,FShe wanted to ensure that those who
OL,18,Fexperienced a similar tragedy were
OL,19,Fable to talk to others who had also
OL,20,Flost a loved one to Sudden Unexpected
OL,21,FDeath in Epilepsy (SUDEP).
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777449958
OL,3,CWoman whose partner died suddenly from
OL,4,Cepilepsy highlights 'invisible'
OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,FThe charity says SUDEP affects all
OL,8,Fages, but particularly those between
OL,9,F20 and 40.
OL,11,FThey say there are around 21 epilepsy-
OL,12,Frelated deaths a week.
OL,14,FThree decades on from Alan's death, Ms
OL,15,FHanna says that there needs to be more
OL,16,Fsupport at government level and a
OL,17,Fbetter understanding of the condition,
OL,18,Fone she did not fully understand
OL,19,Fherself before Alan died.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777449958
OL,3,CWoman whose partner died suddenly from
OL,4,Cepilepsy highlights 'invisible'
OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,FMs Hanna said: "He (Alan) did have
OL,8,Fthree seizures over that period up
OL,9,Funtil the December, when he died in
OL,10,Fhis bed.
OL,12,F"He'd had four seizures in total, they
OL,13,Fwere mostly all at night.
OL,15,F"It was a complete shock to say the
OL,16,Fleast as we'd be told that epilepsy
OL,17,Fwas benign.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777449958
OL,3,CWoman whose partner died suddenly from
OL,4,Cepilepsy highlights 'invisible'
OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,FShe continued: "There are thousands
OL,8,Fand thousands that are connected with
OL,9,Fthe charity now and they're all driven
OL,10,Fby the same concern about injustice
OL,11,Freally, and that this is largely
OL,12,Finvisible and really we have to get
OL,13,Fawareness out there."
OL,15,FThe issues identified by SUDEP Action
OL,16,Fwere discussed at parliamentary level
OL,17,Fon Wednesday 22 April, as Jane's local
OL,18,FMP Olly Glover (Lib Dem, Didcot and
OL,19,FWantage) led a House of Commons debate
OL,20,Fon the subject.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777449958
OL,3,CWoman whose partner died suddenly from
OL,4,Cepilepsy highlights 'invisible'
OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,FDuring the debate, he called for a
OL,8,Fframework to be developed which would
OL,9,Fmean good practice in relation to
OL,10,FSUDEP could be shared to achieve
OL,11,Fbetter outcomes for people.
OL,13,FHe also said that neither epilepsy nor
OL,14,Fneurology is explicitly mentioned in
OL,15,Fthe NHS 10-year plan.
OL,17,FMr Glover also said waiting times
OL,18,Fexperienced by people to attend a
OL,19,Ffirst seizure clinic are "unsafe".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777449958
OL,3,CWoman whose partner died suddenly from
OL,4,Cepilepsy highlights 'invisible'
OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,FIn a statement, a Department of Health
OL,8,Fand Social Care spokesperson said:
OL,9,F"Every death caused by epilepsy is a
OL,10,Ftragedy.
OL,12,F"We are supporting healthcare
OL,13,Fprofessionals provide better diagnoses
OL,14,Fand support for patients through our
OL,15,Ftoolkit and training programme, and
OL,16,Finformation is available online on how
OL,17,Fthe public can respond to epileptic
OL,18,Fseizures and potentially save a life.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
