PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777449958
OL,3,CWoman whose partner died suddenly from
OL,4,Cepilepsy highlights 'invisible'
OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,F"We are also tackling waiting times
OL,8,Ffor treatment through our record
OL,9,Finvestment and modernisation, with
OL,10,Foverall waiting times across the NHS
OL,11,Fnow at their lowest level in three
OL,12,Fyears and A&E performance the best in
OL,13,Fhalf a decade."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
